description: Lists all sessions in your Amazon Web Services account. For more information about sessions, see Store and retrieve conversation history and context with Amazon Bedrock sessions.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: If the total number of results is greater than the maxResults value provided in the request, use this token when making another request in the nextToken field to return the next batch of results.

nested_items.name: sessionSummaries
nested_items.description: A list of summaries for each session in your Amazon Web Services account.

nested_items.name: createdAt
nested_items.description: The timestamp for when the session was created.

nested_items.name: lastUpdatedAt
nested_items.description: The timestamp for when the session was last modified.

nested_items.name: sessionArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the session.

nested_items.name: sessionId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier for the session.

nested_items.name: sessionStatus
nested_items.description: The current status of the session.
